{"tid":1474643,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（極重要） 逃犯條例外，政府又做小動作","createTime":"2019-08-15T08:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T09:25:01.000Z","uid":242263,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a224a1fc84b274b0bfb73affccecf668593d33","tid":1474643,"uid":242263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:57:14.000Z","msg":"當大家仲向到嘈緊逃犯條例時，林鄭已經修改緊中文科課程，唔洗聽同講廣東話了。<br />\n<br />\n16/9諮詢期就過啦，之後拿拿聲上立法會一讀二讀三讀搞點。DQ埋d阻頭阻勢既議員。香港人你慢慢嘈逃犯條例啦，日日食催淚彈啦。<br />\n<br />\n#滅一個文化先滅佢既語言<br />\n#咁既政府管理香港，如果無左示威者，後果會係點？<br />\n#示威者既爆力係唔岩，但哩個政府真係無得救。<br />\n#你可以唔支持黃絲，但有一日香港失去核心價值時，唔好問點解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/whats-new.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcurriculum-development%2Fkla%2Fchi-edu%2Fwhats-new.html&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=5e838410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/whats-new.html</a><br />\n<br />\n16/9終止諮詢的是：<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2FTF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=d2cfe756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"6116754017fd3857e2d4d3346dceb68c0572c57c","tid":1474643,"uid":242263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:57:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f2d163d8e2e09653933e93fb891b06da259ea5ee","tid":1474643,"uid":242263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"eb53cec2580d09d8d5d37d5847259b5445a04e20","tid":1474643,"uid":168214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"